data.description: FHA approved complex!  This beautiful 2 bedroom unit features 2 full baths.  A nice open floor plan!  Beautiful floors throughout this lovely patio home.  Great counter and breakfast bar space.  Black appliances remain.  The Great Room and Dining Area feature vaulted ceilings and beautiful trim work.  There is a gas fireplace.  The primary bedroom has a walk in closet and private bathroom.  There is a great private patio in the back of the home to enjoy being outside.
